





	
                
                Parameter Tree:

                
                    EARTH SCIENCE > ATMOSPHERE > AEROSOLS > AEROSOL OPTICAL DEPTH/THICKNESS

                    

                
                Definition:

                
                    The degree to which Aerosols prevent light from passing through. Optical
depth/thickness depends upon the physical constitution ,the form, and the
concentration of particles. 
                
                

                

                
